<https://eliascrum.github.io/eliascrum/id/publication/urinary-coliphages-2023> ec:summary "Catalogs urinary E. coli phage diversity and shows that multiple urinary and non-urinary coliphages can lyse urinary E. coli strains, supporting a role for phages in shaping urobiome composition." .
